{"word":"H7430 - רָמַשׂ - râmas - raw-mas' - Creep","slug":"H7430","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָמַשׂ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râmas"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-mas'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Creep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05DE;&#x05E9;&#x05C2; - ra&#x0302;mas&#x0301;</b> - <i>raw-mas'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>glide</i> swiftly, that is, to <i>crawl</i> or <i>move</i> with short steps; by analogy to <i>swarm: - </i>creep, move."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7431\">H7431</a>"}]}